  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>These gloves are invisible while worn.</p><p></p><p>The gloves have 5 charges that reset at dawn.</p><p></p><p>These gloves grant two abilites.</p><ol><li><p><strong>Master Thief</strong> (Consumes 1 charge)</p><ol><li><p>Gain +5 to your next Sleight of Hand Check</p></li><li><p>Lock Sense - You can magically determine if a lock is trapped and gain immediate knowledge as to the difficulty of picking it.</p></li></ol></li><li><p><strong>Pop Lock</strong> (Consumes 2 charges)</p><ol><li><p>Allows automatic success at picking a lock.</p></li></ol></li></ol><p></p>",
